Name: Markouts
Description: Markout Curves starting at SpreadPNL at time zero. Those curve represent the PnL of counterparty

Name: MarkoutsAtZero
Description: Markout Curves starting at 0 at time 0. Those curves represent price impact curves and do not include Spread Paid.

Name: MarkoutsAtZeroAverage
Description: Average (as opposed to weighted average) version of MarkoutsAtZero.

Name: Volatilities
Description: Standard deviationof each markout point for confidence intervals
